description:
This 2 bedrooms’ luxury condo, hardwood floors and open kitchen layout. 

Located on a quiet street, the building stands out as the prettiest, being it brand new. 

Lots of natural light and stylish furniture. 

Subway is 2 blocks away and can be connected to Downtown in less of 15 min. Subway 24hrs. If you desire, no need of car rental to communicate.

Brooklyn Standards have definitely been raised. 

No detail were spared for this beautiful 2br condo. 

Each room has a full size bed, mirror, nightstand and closet space. 

Perfect for shared and families alike.

The kitchen is very modern and bright, including an oven, dishwasher and microwave.

Sink in the bathtub for a warm bath.!

On the 4th floor, we have an amazing roof deck

Enjoy the sunset! :)

You have full access to the apartment. It will be private for you.

I'm always available via Airbnb messaging

Bushwick is one of the coolest neighborhoods in Brooklyn. And you'll be in the heart of it.
Steps to many local shops, restaurants and great bars. 
You can view amazing graffiti work all over the place. 
Bushwick is the house of Bushwick Open Studio when artists, musicians and residents alike open up shop, close street and it's just a big party with art galleries.
Many restaurants are owned by small families or locals alike and are just amazing.
Bushwick, cool is just and understatement

M train to Central Av Station is just 2 short blocks

I long for views always.
I recommend heading to the roof top and check sunsets and sunrises

review.comments: Luis' place is great. It's super quiet and peaceful. Luis was proactive in making sure our needs were fully met. Everything is new construction with new finishes as it is located in a reviving part of Brooklyn (Bushwick).  Easy walk to local delis, grocery and bars.  Great value for locating just a few miles from the heart of NYC via the subway and saving a LOT of $$$.
